      {
        "Language": "ENG",
        "Name": "Blasted Basarios!",
        "Client": "Sandy Plains Miner",
        "Description": "*cough* Dang Basarios! *wheeze*\r\nOne minute you\u0027re sittin\u0027 on what\r\nyou thought was a rock, tryin\u0027 to\r\nget the dirt out of yer boots, *hack*\r\nand the next, you\u0027re huffin\u0027 *cough*\r\nall kinds of who-knows-what!\r\n*hack*",
